high_descs: Turn left and move to the end of the island above the trash can.
Pick up the green apple from the counter.
Turn left and move across the room to the microwave on the left.
Warm the apple in the microwave for a few seconds and then take it back out.
Turn left and head back to the end of the island where the trash can is located.
Throw the apple into the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed up apple in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn left walk towards the counter in front of the trash bin
Pick up the apple on the counter
Turn left the right and head to the microwave on your left
Open the microwave put in and out the apple then close the microwave
Turn left walk forward then turn left face the trash bin
Drop the apple in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Put the heather apple in the trash bin

high_descs: Turn to the left, and then left again to face the trash can.
Pick up the apple from the island on the closer side.
Carry the apple and turn to the left and then right. Look up to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the apple inside. Shut the door. Open the door and take out the apple. Shut the door.
Carry the apple and turn to the left, then the left again to face the trash can.
Place the apple in the trash can on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Heat an apple and throw it away.
